    "target": "_blank",
    "rel": "noreferrer"
  }, "OUR UP-TO-DATE ROADMAP ON GITHUB"), "."), mdx("p", null, "Having a more recent database engine is always worthwhile, so I\u2019m definitely looking forward to the PostgreSQL 12 compatibility. The other ones are online schema migrations, full ALTER TABLE support, and more day two operations documentation and guides."), mdx("h2", {
    "id": "have-you-looked-at-other-distributed-sql-or-distributed-databases-in-addition-to-yugabytedb"
