  }, "WHAT ADVICE WOULD YOU GIVE THEM?"), mdx("p", null, "If you need PostgreSQL and plan for scale, definitely consider YugabyteDB. It will take you from a single node to global scale with little-to-no effort. My advice would be to read through the documentation first. The documentation covers a lot of interesting aspects of the system and that knowledge will be beneficial long-term."), mdx("h2", {
