  }, "ANYTHING ELSE YOU WOULD LIKE PEOPLE TO KNOW?"), mdx("p", null, "Erlang is awesome for learning functional programming. Tests and documentation aren\u2019t boring. Integration tests are better than unit tests. Don\u2019t assume, talk to your users."));
